            <h1><!-- 需要回答的问题1 -->
                How will you begin to dream something no machine can dream?
            </h1>
            <img src="assets/images/blur.png" alt="blur of pink ellipse" min-width="800px">
        </div>
        <div class="row"><!-- 问题1答案 -->
            <h4>
                I think I'll start with regret. It is precisely those imperfect moments that make up each and every one of us vivid and lively. Regret represents not only the memory point of "still a little short of perfection", but also a kind of tension. The direction of "leaving no regrets" has endowed us with the motivation for many actions. Of course, this kind of "leaving no regrets" doesn't necessarily mean striving to achieve something or creating a wonderful life. It can also be enjoying the present time to the fullest or taking a break to relax and rest to not waste one's energy. In short, it is to achieve some kind of satisfaction.
            </h4>
            <br>
            <img src="assets/images/imperfect.png" alt="imperfect" min-width="800px">
